'''Brathflen Corporation''' was an [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorian]]-owned corporation that was the manufacturer of the [[Manollium-class herdship|''Manollium''-class Herdship]]. Around [[17 BBY/Legends|17 BBY]] they came to [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]]; in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]] they erected a dome over [[Plawal Rift]].

